  <brief_title>A Conversion Study of Immediate Release (IR) and Modified Release (MR) Forms of Topiramate (TPM)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Conversion Study to Determine the Relative Bioavailability of TPM MR vs TPM IR in Subjects With Epilepsy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
