  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This multi-center, two-treatment study compares the pharmacokinetic profiles of Immediate
      Release (IR) and Modified Release (MR) formulations of Topiramate (TPM) in patients with
      epilepsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
